- f) measures to promote education and training, including non-formal education and training, as well as awareness raising activities on gender equality and unconscious gender bias for all age groups in order to combat occupational segregation; and
- g) specific measures for gender-neutral job evaluation, highlighting the benefits of such evaluation for employers.
